                  <tr>
                    <td height="19" colspan="2" align="left" valign="top" class="content"><span class="titles_red_14">NYFA EVENTS Screen archives:<br />
                    </span><span class="white_content_notbold">&gt; <a href="/film/press/la_events/wedding.htm">" Wedding Crashers" Monday, August 8th</a><br />
